module.name: Win32Int

element.name: IDC_IBEAM
element.short: I-Beam cursor, often used with text controls.

element.name: LclCursorToWin32CursorMap
element.short: Table mapping LCL cursor constants into Windows cursors.

element.name: SKIP_LMCHANGE
element.short: Flag used to avoid propagating LM_CHANGE for TCustomCheckBox.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet
element.short: The Windows interface class, derived from TWidgetSet.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.FAppHandle
element.short: The parent of all windows, represents the button of the taskbar.
element.descr: This window also is the owner of the clipboard. Assoc. windowproc also acts as handler for popup menus.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.SetAppHandle
element.short: Sets the application window handle, if not done before.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.SetCallback
element.short: Installs an callback for a Lazarus message Msg for Sender[???]

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppInit
element.short: Initializes the application on the platform, returns Screen information.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppMinimize
element.short: Minimizes the whole application to the taskbar.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppRestore
element.short: Restore application previously minimized to the taskbar.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppBringToFront
element.short: Brings the entire application on top of all other non-topmost programs.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppWaitMessage
element.short: Waits for arrival of a message.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppTerminate
element.descr: Not implemented as: Tells Windows to halt and destroy[?]

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppSetIcon
element.short: Set the icon of the taskbar button.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppSetTitle
element.short: Set the title of the taskbar button.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppSetVisible
element.short: Change the visibility of the application window.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppRemoveStayOnTopFlags
element.short: Resets all StayOnTop windows to NoTopmost.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppRestoreStayOnTopFlags
element.short: Sets all windows in the StayOnTop list to TopMost.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.AppSetMainFormOnTaskBar
element.short: Make the MainForm (in)visible in the TaskBar (exchange with application window).

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.InitStockFont
element.short: Initializes a font object to an (predefined) stock font.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.DCSetPixel
element.short: Set the color of a pixel on a canvas.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.DCGetPixel
element.short: Get the color of a pixel on a canvas.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.CreateTimer
element.short: Creates an timer with the given callback method.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.HandleWakeMainThread
element.short: Wake up GUI thread by sending a message to it.

element.name: TWin32WidgetSet.DefaultFont
element.short: The default font of the platform.

element.name: Win32WidgetSet
element.short: Typed alias for the generic WidgetSet variable.

element.name: WindowProc
element.short: The WndProc of all LCL windows.
element.descr: Translates Windows messages into LCL messages. Invokes the target Dispatch() or "Intf..." methods.

element.name: CallDefaultWindowProc
element.short: Passes message on to 'default' handler. This can be a control specific window procedure or the default window procedure.

module.short: The Windows interface for the LCL.
